在宣布回归之前他与诺埃尔一起拍摄的照片</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-oasis-reuniting-for-huge-london-and-manchester-shows-3786823">并暗示乐队在正式宣布之前将在曼彻斯特进行一些大型演出</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="利亚姆·加拉格尔 | 利亚姆·加拉格尔展示和讲述" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RNCZO0H1kgw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p>最近，他还开玩笑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-rumours-of-richard-ashcroft-supporting-oasis-on-reunion-tour-3793657">说</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/richard-ashcroft">理查德·阿什克罗夫特</a>和卡斯特都有可能支持绿洲， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-richard-ashcroft-as-special-guest-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3804758">这两者</a>最终都再次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-cast-as-final-support-act-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3806934">成为正式的</a>。</p><p>到目前为止，巡演包括明年夏天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">在英国和爱尔兰举行的一系列大型体育场演出</a>，不久之后还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-extra-dates-to-north-american-2025-reunion-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3799159">在北美</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">南美</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">澳大利亚</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-south-korean-and-japan-dates-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3814881">韩国和日本</a>进行巡演。</p><p>在得知他们将回归后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269">Oasis 排除了在 2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上进行头条表演的可能性</a>，并表示明年夏天他们不会出现在任何其他音乐节上。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-oasis-return-to-knebworth-in-2026-3792709">利亚姆和诺埃尔也驳斥了 2026 年重返纳贝沃斯的传言</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-there-could-be-an-album-from-oasis-if-we-nail-this-tour-and-be-kind-to-one-another-3823699">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 的帖子称，“如果我们能做好这次巡演并善待彼此”，Oasis“可能会出一张专辑”，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
